        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2235010243" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer651583015458266218">A seemingly simple story of two children walking home from a visit to their grandmother grows in scope and meaning as one thinks about it. Great descriptive writing from observations of landscapes and weather to human quirks and a touch of humor. Warning: The introduction by W.H. Auden (and even the back cover) have spoilers.<br/></span>

          </span>
