          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer251440354" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12350032257396423158">This Christmas story reminded me of Hans Christian Andersen&apos;s longer tales , such as The Snow Queen and The Little Mermaid, except that the supernatural is the natural world of Alpine peaks and glaciers, snow and stars. A pleasant Christmas read.</span>
  <span id="freeText12350032257396423158" style="display:none">This Christmas story reminded me of Hans Christian Andersen's longer tales , such as The Snow Queen and The Little Mermaid, except that the supernatural is the natural world of Alpine peaks and glaciers, snow and stars. A pleasant Christmas read.</span>
  <a data-text-id="12350032257396423158" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


